      "span_text": "accounting controls [CITATION_1] . The ASX Corporate Governance Council (2003) recommends the establishment of an audit committee that is of 'sufficient size, independence and technical expertise to discharge its mandate effectively' (ASX Corporate Governance Council, 2003)."
